      <title>莫迪领导的政党赢得关键州选举，印度股市延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/india-stocks-extend-rally-as-modi-s-party-wins-key-state-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党领导的联盟在印度最富裕的马哈拉施特拉邦取得压倒性胜利，印度股市基准指数周一飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/india-stocks-extend-rally-as-modi-s-party-wins-key-state-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 04:02:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大日本印刷称 Elliott 已出售其大部分股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/dai-nippon-printing-says-elliott-has-sold-most-of-its-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大日本印刷株式会社 (Dai Nippon Printing Co.) 表示，Elliott Investment Management 似乎大幅减持了该公司股份，而这距离该激进基金购买该公司股份还不到两年。该消息导致该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/dai-nippon-printing-says-elliott-has-sold-most-of-its-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 03:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国指控引发股价暴跌后，阿达尼宣称拥有充足现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/adani-touts-sufficient-cash-after-rout-sparked-by-us-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度阿达尼集团表示，其拥有足够的现金来偿还债务，此前美国对创始人高塔姆·阿达尼的贿赂起诉引发了该集团股票和债券的抛售，该集团试图安抚债权人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/adani-touts-sufficient-cash-after-rout-sparked-by-us-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 02:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员将注意力转向美联储下一步行动，黄金价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/gold-steady-after-surging-last-week-on-escalation-of-ukraine-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们忽略了美元走软并将注意力转向美联储即将公布的利率决定，黄金价格在上周创下 20 个月来最大涨幅后出现下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/gold-steady-after-surging-last-week-on-escalation-of-ukraine-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 00:16:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票、债券价格因交易员青睐 Bessent 而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-falls-as-treasury-pick-tempers-trump-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票和国债价格上涨，交易员对唐纳德·特朗普选择斯科特·贝森特担任财政部长表示欢迎，认为这一慎重选择将为美国经济和金融市场注入更多稳定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/dollar-falls-as-treasury-pick-tempers-trump-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 22:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼指控特朗普试图让印度留在美国轨道上的愿望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/adani-charges-to-test-trump-s-desire-to-keep-india-in-us-orbit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2018年，中国科技巨头华为技术有限公司一名高管因违反美国法律被捕，此举震惊了国家主席习近平的核心圈子，并引发了人们对唐纳德·特朗普是否会介入此案的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/adani-charges-to-test-trump-s-desire-to-keep-india-in-us-orbit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
